<table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5" bgcolor="#6D6D6D" class='forumpostcontent'>
  <tr>
    <td class='forumpostcontent'>If anyone has some good macros they want to share, post them here.  I'm going to start experimenting with a Sampling/Rest macro.  The basic commands will look something like this:<br />
<br />
/stand<br />
/sample<br />
/pause 300<br />
/sit<br />
/pause 300<br />
<br />
I need to fine tune the pause intervals (300 seconds = 5 minutes), and figure out the best way to repeat it.  <br />
<br />
A couple things to figure out first:<br />
<br />
1.  Does the inactivity timer consider <i>macro use</i> as "activity" or "inactivity" when the mouse and keyboard are not touched?<br />
<br />
2.  How large/long can a single macro be?<br />
<br />
3.  What kind of options do we have for looping, stacking, and aliasing macros?<br><br>
        <!-- BEGIN TEMPLATE: postbit_signature -->
