    <td class='forumpostcontent'>Once you cap on experience at Survey IV, the only advantage you get is a raw material while you sleep.  The risk is that you may die while AFK... but so far, every time I die, all my gear dies with me. I have never had to go find my corpse to loot my gear back. My clone is activated in full gear. I'm guessing SOE has not fully implemented death yet.<br />
<br />
If you have a machine out in the field sampling for you, you achieve the same thing. You get raw materials while you sleep.  If sample looping is an exploit, it's only a minor one that won't matter much after you get into the 2nd tier professions.<br><br>
