    <td class='forumpostcontent'>Now... there is a UI command (/ui) that let's us call a toolbar and activate a button on it (toolbarSlot##). I wonder if there are specific UI names for other UI items?  If there is a name for each bar, menu, or option window that comes up in the UI then we can begin to program complex macros that will do just about anything.  I'd love to come up with a macro that builds something in a crafting tool...<br><br>
